my final project ideas

1.An e-commerce store and review site for skin care products.
 

FOR:Women of all ages who wants to look  good and feel good.


WHO: who are looking for online convenient store with genuine reviews on product and brands from real users on skin care products etc. 


USP/BRAND is: An e-commerce platform for top brands and genuine reviews on skin care products etc.




THAT: An e-commerce store and a review site that  provides opportunity for women of all ages who wants to look good and feel good and has money to spend on top quality skin care products.

  

BY: Given buyers the opportunity to hear from real users a product, knowing what other people are saying about a product before they buy.  



BECAUSE: This ensures easy way of buying and quality assurance of products.
